DarkMouse::
"Who's this Mikey guy you speak of? Never mind. Anyway, Look, you got 
a great peice of maximal there. Think about it. What do maximals do? 
They care." Holds hands in a mock angelic pose," Those little goodie 
goodies can't help themselves when it comes to trying to save one of 
thier own. Now, we are all preds. You two, me, Galvatron over here,", 
pointing to Galvatron, "and Neptune. We are all working for the same 
thing. Wiping out Maximals Right? Well, then let's work together and 
wipe some out. Now that you have that cat over there, we can use it 
for bait. Set a trap, make the maxi's come to us and then we spring 
the trap, and kill them at our leasure. Like shooting fish in a water 
tank.  What do you say? Want to have some fun killing a few Maximals?"
Deplomicy wasn't one of her strong suits, but here, she was really 
trying to pull this off. IF she could convince them to use the cat as 
bait, then maybe Galvatron would trust her enough to give her the 
codes she could finish learning all there was in the data bases of 
that ship.
